OL,3,CThree-quarters of rivers in poor
OL,4,Cecological health, citizen scientists
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThree-quarters of UK rivers were found
OL,8,Fto be in poor ecological health by
OL,9,Fcitizen scientists who took samples
OL,10,Ffrom waterways across the UK.
OL,12,FThousands of people measured their
OL,13,Flocal water quality between June 7 and
OL,14,F10, collecting 1,300 datasets as part
OL,15,Fof the Great UK WaterBlitz campaign
OL,16,Forganised by environmental charity
OL,17,FEarthwatch Europe.
