OL,4,Cecological health, citizen scientists
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FSasha Woods, the charity's director of
OL,8,Fscience and policy, said: "These
OL,9,Fresults are truly disturbing ` there
OL,10,Fare no parts of the UK unaffected by
OL,11,Fnutrient pollution.
OL,13,F"The picture around London and the
OL,14,FThames river basin is particularly
OL,15,Fdire.
OL,17,F"Our rivers have been historically
OL,18,Fstressed by farming, and we're seeing
OL,19,Fthis being made worse by inappropriate
OL,20,For limited sewage treatment.
