OL,4,Cecological health, citizen scientists
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"The Government has committed to
OL,8,Fprotect 30% of land for nature by 2030
OL,9,F` that will be meaningless if the
OL,10,Frivers and streams running through the
OL,11,Fland, the arteries of life, are
OL,12,Fdiseased."
OL,14,FThe charity said the testing programme
OL,15,Fmirrors some of the outcomes from a
OL,16,Frecent report by the Office for
OL,17,FEnvironmental Protection (OEP), which
OL,18,Ffound "most of England's water bodies
OL,19,Fare in an unsatisfactory state".
