OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"The next government must commit to a
OL,8,Fnational strategy for freshwater that
OL,9,Fincludes all forms of pollution and is
OL,10,Fbacked by a properly-resourced
OL,11,Forganisation that makes use of rich
OL,12,Fcitizen science data."
OL,14,FThe latest official Water Framework
OL,15,FDirective monitoring shows that 17% of
OL,16,Fwater bodies are in a poor state, 63%
OL,17,Fare in an average state (moderate) and
OL,18,F16% are in good state.
